# First-Agent LLM API KEYS — consumed ONLY by the fa-egress-proxy container.
#
# Deploy location: /srv/first-agent/secrets/fa.env (host, mode 0600, OUTSIDE the
# repo and OUTSIDE the agent's /workspace). Mounted read-only into the
# fa-egress-proxy container at /run/secrets/fa.env. The agent (first-agent)
# container NEVER mounts this file and never receives these values — it reaches
# providers only through the proxy, which injects the real key at the transport
# layer (ADR-12, egress-injection proxy).
#
# Коротко для оператора:
# 1. Редактируйте РЕАЛЬНЫЕ ключи только здесь: /srv/first-agent/secrets/fa.env
# 2. Не коммитьте этот файл.
# 3. Агент этот файл не видит; его читает только контейнер fa-egress-proxy.
# 4. Имена переменных должны совпадать с api_key_env в /srv/first-agent/routing/models.yaml
# 5. После изменения ключей пересоздайте стек: scripts/fa-update.sh
#
# NEVER commit this file. Uncomment and fill in the providers you actually use.
# Names MUST match the api_key_env fields in /srv/first-agent/routing/models.yaml.

# Primary providers (used by models.yaml.example)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-CHANGEME
# FIREWORKS_API_KEY=fw-CHANGEME

# Additional providers (uncomment as needed)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-CHANGEME
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-CHANGEME
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_CHANGEME
# TOGETHER_API_KEY=together-CHANGEME
# XAI_API_KEY=xai-CHANGEME
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk-CHANGEME
# PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=pplx-CHANGEME
# NVIDIA_BUILD_API_KEY=nvapi-CHANGEME
# GITHUB_MODELS_API_KEY=ghp_CHANGEME
# MODAL_API_KEY=ak-CHANGEME
# LAMBDA_LABS_API_KEY=lambda-CHANGEME
